{"tid":1969092,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解人越老越糊塗？","createTime":"2020-04-12T07:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T16:07:02.000Z","uid":134180,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"865f9b708d0aefd145f7fef94ae0addb4ffb7b1d","tid":1969092,"uid":134180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"鑑於肺炎關係，老媽子剛好冇得撈，日日留係屋企煩住晒，唔知係咪人老左既關係，覺得佢真係越老越糊塗，諗埋D奇怪既野，矯正佢仲要唔抵得比人話番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子： 皇冠牌出左隻可以抹坐廁消毒個隻濕紙巾，老媽子話可以買番去屋企用，根住我話番佢，係屋企用黎做咩？搞好D清潔仲實際啦！依D野for番出街公廁個D地方用！然後佢又唔鐘意人地話佢，仲要話轉我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係想死，諗D野治標唔治本，本末倒置。<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇得分享多d人越老越糊塗既例子。"},{"pid":"3fd674181309dc580d56369128f633717ae3d4cc","tid":1969092,"uid":58867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T09:04:17.000Z","msg":"點解人會死？"},{"pid":"8923c7d75e8eed62f5c5bad7f990f456a108378f","tid":1969092,"uid":23699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:54:47.000Z","msg":"有無諗過佢不嬲係咁？"},{"pid":"cd764eb1f70befb1dd07fae6fee76cc02c93b160","tid":1969092,"uid":134180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8923c7d75e8eed62f5c5bad7f990f456a108378f","tid":1969092,"uid":23699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:54:47.000Z","msg":"有無諗過佢不嬲係咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"年輕時冇咁唔用腦既，依家個腦似停頓左咁。<br />\n係咪人老左都會咁？定個腦開始有毛病？"},{"pid":"da4a3882e1d82b77369c09944d49c20b99917702","tid":1969092,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"睇人者<br />\n<br />\n我個名果個不知幾心水清"},{"pid":"c94fa11145e00d9c5b2c26ef557613863640600b","tid":1969092,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd764eb1f70befb1dd07fae6fee76cc02c93b160","tid":1969092,"uid":134180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8923c7d75e8eed62f5c5bad7f990f456a108378f","tid":1969092,"uid":23699,"like":2,